text: Kara Elizabeth Drew (born July 15, 1975) is an American professional wrestler and valet. She is best known for her time with World Wrestling Entertainment (WWE), where she was known by the ring name Cherry. During her time there, she was known for being the manager of the tag team Deuce 'n Domino and was also a wrestler on WWE's SmackDown brand. Drew was released from her WWE contract on August 15, 2008. After being released, Drew started working at SeaWorld. ==Championships== *Jersey Championship Wrestling **JCW Women's Championship (one time) *Women Superstars Uncensored **WSU/NWS King and Queen Tournament (2005) (with Julio Dinero) *Pro Wrestling Illustrated **She was ranked #27 of the best 50 female singles wrestlers in the PWI Female 50 in 2008. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:American professional wrestlers Category:Female professional wrestlers Category:Former WWE wrestlers Category:People from Morristown, New Jersey Category:Professional wrestling managers and valets Category:Sportspeople from New Jersey
